# Keep the build context small + the image clean. We never copy apps/web source
# (the Dockerfile only COPYs apps/api + packages/contracts), and node_modules is
# always reinstalled inside the image via `npm ci`.
**/node_modules
.git
.github
.next
**/.next
coverage
**/coverage
**/*.log
**/.env
**/.env.local
ARCHITECTURE.md
MASTER-PROPOSAL.md
EXECUTION-PLAYBOOK.md
PRODUCT-POSITIONING.md
DEVELOPMENT-LOG.md
apps/web/scripts/*.json

apps/api/dist

# Plan 006: tests live in <workspace>/tests/ — never shipped to prod images.
# The runtime bundle is esbuild-built from src/server.ts and never reaches
# test files, but excluding tests/ keeps the build context small + clean.
**/tests

# Plan 007 phase 0: generated test artifacts (junit, json, coverage)
# never belong in a production image. The runtime bundle was already
# clean via esbuild reachability; excluding .artifacts/ makes it
# explicit + keeps the build context small.
.artifacts
